# Copy to .env.production (or set in CI) before `npm run build`.
# Single gateway URL for SPA + API (reverse-proxy merges /api/Auth → Tenant, /api → MatOps).
# Example: https://erp.example.com/api  (no trailing slash on host; path includes /api if your gateway serves API under /api)
# VITE_API_URL=https://erp.example.com/api
